All pictures and wording are simple to personalize. (IMAGE PLACEMENT TIP: An easy way to center a photo exactly how you want is to crop it before uploading to the Zazzle website.) This template can be customized with any details of your choice, such as party invitation info, parents’ names, special honors, degree title, favorite inspirational quote, graduate’s contact info, future education plans, or new job position. Please note that gold is printed color, not metallic foil. These elegant graduation announcement cards are a trendy and chic way to share your special day celebration with family and friends.
